Well, what do we have here? The usurper I’ve been hearing so many rumbles about?
Uh, who are you supposed to be?
You dominated my Tickle Lords with your meddling in my domain, so you’ve forced the Tickle Monarch herself to bestir herself! Tis I, Tickle Queen Royanna!

The Tickle Queen strides forward. She’s a striking figure, statue-esque, tall, and straight-backed, despite the curly silver hair that indicates a certain maturity. Her golden crown shimmers in the pale light, and her soft green eyes are narrow with malice. Her face is heavy with makeup, including pale blue eye shadow, and her ornate dress is a regal purple.
I’m not sure ‘dominated’ is quite the right word for what transpired...
One of the Queen's guards speaks up, with her hand on a strange sword.
Save your excuses and beseech the Queen for mercy! This is your one chance to surrender!
Through service, you can redeem yourself for your wickedness.
Erm, can we think about it? Maybe decline for now and get back to you later?
No. The Queen’s orders are absolute. You have no say in the matter.

She waves her hand, and your knees shake, pulled inexorably to the ground till you find yourself kneeling. Seconds later, your arms disobey you and stretch out onto the ground, so you’re more than kneeling — you’re kowtowing, an utter and complete display of submission. Why is your body rebelling against you? There’s something about this woman’s haughty bearing, an overbearing presence that sends every nerve against you. To go against her wishes is incomprehensible, beyond impossible, like a world where two plus two equals ten.
I shall now accept your oaths of eternal loyalty and service. You’ve disrupted my operations in this region, but that is no matter. You shall set my world to rights...
Do you swear to serve me now and forever?
Very well. Anoint them with the royal oils!

The two guards step forward, removing flasks from their hip and also removing your footwear. With your arms outstretched and you on your knees, it’s easy for the guards to apply the oil on your bare soles and slap it on your armpits. You can feel the cool, queasy sensation as the liquid seeps into your flesh — already, even the air is beginning to tickle.
Let the process begin. Let them taste the royal swords.

You hear the sound of metal escaping its sheath. For a moment, you wonder if you’re going to be struck down, and whacked with the weapons, but you’ve forgotten what kind of game this is — The weapon tingles, tingles unlike anything you’ve ever experienced. It’s like the blade is reaching directly into the nerves in your feet and stimulating them with the force of a thunderbolt. It feels like brushes, combs, and pinwheels, all mixed into one! As the tip of the blade carves down from your heel to the ridge under your toes, you shriek with laughter. And your feet aren’t even that ticklish! Even with your head down, you can make out Cissy howling and writhing beside you.

The edges of the sword brush your arches, and you gasp and groan. If the tip was poor intensity, the sides are pure stimulant. They feel like feathers and tongues and kisses all mixed with a shot of vodka to your system, and you feel dazed, drunk, and giggly as it brushes up to your toes. You feel a growing urgency between your legs, an urgency that loses its footing and goes tripping to the ground when the point of the sword jabs into your armpits, with the guard’s sharp nails taking over the scratching of your feet.
Ahahahahah, tohohohoo muhuhuhuch! It tihihihickles! Mehehercy!

You shudder and tremble, but your limbs refuse to move, as the guard’s sword and sharp nails explore your body with utter impunity. You can hear Cissy’s squealing beside you, and you can only imagine it to be even worse, with those hypersensitive small feet of hers.

Not until we are finished, but you are making the right noises now. Continue, my faithful guards. I believe the female might enjoy the tip of a sword around those small wiggling toes of hers. And the male, well… I can see the bulge in his britches. Set them free, and let’s see how ticklish he is down there...
You fight even harder, but even with your entire body shaking, your arms and legs stubborn ignore you and refuse to move.
Stay still for your Queen. I shall not hear another word from your mouth, only dreadful laughter!

The tickling goes on for so long and so intense, that you can feel your brain shutting down. Nothing seems real, nothing seems to exist, aside from your genitals, your feet, and your armpits. When the torment final stops and the Tickle Queen commands you to stand, you look very different from the villagers you were at the start of the journey.
You are conscripted, my new Tickle Lords.
Well, maybe this won’t be so bad...
Yeah, this magic feels oddly familiar...
So when do we get to tickle you, Queenie?
Me? Perhaps as an immense reward for future service... I shall not allow myself to be touched, even by one of my own Lords.
As a reward for leal service, you may get an answer in time.
Damn, what a tease. And I can see the credits preparing to roll! Pretty evil sequel hook...
Yeah, these games already do stuff like that. Phooey! But it has been a pretty fun journey, so I can’t complain too much...
As you return to dreary reality, you shower and then head straight to bed for a siesta, and you have a good idea where you’ll end up next...
